Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:18.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケーニッヒ）ケ〜ッケッケッケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:22.88,Flashback,Koenig,0,0,0,,The great sorcerer Koenig has \Ncome to pay his respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:22.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔人ケーニッヒ様が\N挨拶に来てやったぜ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.75,Flashback,Koenig,0,0,0,,Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:24.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,レオン！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:28.38,Flashback,Koenig,0,0,0,,I will defeat you and become \Nthe Demon Lord myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:28.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様を倒して 俺様が魔王になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:30.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心して死ね！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.34,Flashback,Koenig,0,0,0,,You can die with your mind at ease!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:35.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（レオン）\N小物が… 誰の差し金やら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:34.87,Flashback,Leon,0,0,0,,Who sent a lowly creature like you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが ちょうどいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.44,Flashback,Leon,0,0,0,,Still, this is a fine opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:40.84,Flashback,Leon,0,0,0,,Your turn has come, Ifrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.60,0:02:39.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（レオン）出番だぞ\N（シズ）え？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（レオン）イフリート
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:43.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（レオン）どうした？\N（シズ）あっ… え？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:43.03,Flashback,Leon,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:51.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ケーニッヒ）\Nくう〜 ナメやがって！\N俺様を無視するとは！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:51.16,Flashback,Koenig,0,0,0,,You're ignoring me?! \NYou'll regret underestimating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:56.66,Flashback,Koenig,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to die first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:56.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先に死にたいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:59.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろう 死にやがれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.20,Flashback,Koenig,0,0,0,,Very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.87,Flashback,Koenig,0,0,0,,Go ahead and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:19.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフ… これは面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:19.98,Flashback,Leon,0,0,0,,Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.23,Flashback,Leon,0,0,0,,What did you say your name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:25.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（レオン）\Nお前の名前は何だったかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.88,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,Shizu...e.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しず… え…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズ… エ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:31.33,Flashback,Leon,0,0,0,,Shizu E?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:32.53,Flashback,Leon,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:32.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふむ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:35.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日より“シズ”と名乗るがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:35.76,Flashback,Leon,0,0,0,,As of today, you will be called Shizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:37.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シズ）シズ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:37.90,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,Shizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:50.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ピリノ）\Nフフフ… たくさん食べてね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:50.24,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,Eats lots, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:59.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっ この子\N親と はぐれたみたいで…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.80,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,I-It got separated from its mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.77,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,P-Please pretend you didn't see this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:01.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… お願い 見逃して！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.83,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:07.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰にも言わないよ\N私も一緒に お世話していい？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.27,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,Can I take care of it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん！　もちろん！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:11.65,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食べた 食べた！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.26,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,He's eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わあ… ねえ この子の名前は？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:20.74,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,So what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:23.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔物に名前はないんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.66,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,Monsters don't have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:26.17,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,But it's sad to have no name to go by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:26.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シズ）\N名前がないのは かわいそうだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この子も そう言ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.34,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,See? He agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“ピズ”って どうかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:32.46,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,How about Pizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.50,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,Pizu... That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:35.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ピズ… いいかも！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねっ ピズ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.22,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,Right, Pizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:43.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか大きくなった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.40,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,Look! He got bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:46.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ… 大きくなった！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.48,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,You got bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:52.71,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,Pirino, you know you can't \Ntake Pizu to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:52.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シズ）\Nピリノ ダメだよ\N勝手に お城に連れてきちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:55.49,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. He's really smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ　この子 賢いし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:57.32,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シズ）でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.25,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,He's really friendly with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:05:01.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ピリノ）\Nこんなに懐いてるんだよ\N使い魔として認めてくれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.66,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'll let him be my familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.33,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:09.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ピリノ）\Nあっ… どうしたの？　ピズ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:09.42,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Pizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:12.70,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,It's okay... Come on, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だよ 大丈夫だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねっ 落ち着いて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.79,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,Just calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.43,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,Be good, now... Pizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい子だから… ピズ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.93,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,It's okay... It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ピリノ）大丈夫… 大丈夫だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.91,Flashback,Pirino,0,0,0,,Shizu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.50,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,Enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:39.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ピリノ）いやあああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:44.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:52.88,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,What... did I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今… 何を…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.83,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,M-My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かっ 体…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体が勝手に…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.18,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,My body moved on its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:03.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,炎で… 私は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:01.27,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,The flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:04.91,Flashback,Shizu,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は… うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハア ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぐっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:07:00.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\N俺たちの町\N気に入ってもらえたかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:07:00.08,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,So, do you like our town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ とっても！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.24,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,Yes, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:10.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nシズさんさえよかったら\Nいつまでだって いていいんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.89,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,You're welcome to stay\Nas long as you'd like, Shizu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シズ）ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.59,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:15.15,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,but I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも… 行かなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.32,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:16.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:20.38,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,If I stay here, I might \Nbring trouble for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:20.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シズ）\Nここにいたら\N迷惑をかけちゃうかもしれないし
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の旅の目的は…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:26.43,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,The goal of my journey is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:27.93,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:32.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シズ）私を召喚した男を捜すこと
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.73,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,...to find the man who summoned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\N見つけたら どうするんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.08,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,What will you do when you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:45.95,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Well, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:48.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった！　残念だけど\Nいつでも遊びに来てくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:48.54,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,It's too bad, but you can come visit anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:49.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歓迎するよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.82,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,You'll always be welcome! Right, Ranga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なっ ランガ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.00,Main,Ranga,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:51.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ランガ）もちろんです！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:54.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.34,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:07:59.71,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,Thank you, too, Ranga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ランガも ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:11.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレン）\Nシズさん\N一緒にブルムンドに戻りません？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:11.73,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Shizu, why don't you come \Nback to Blumund with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:12.53,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.04,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,It'd be awfully sad to say goodbye here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレン）\Nここで さよならなんて寂しいです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シズ）\Nあなたたちは いい冒険者だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.72,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,You're all exceptional adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:23.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒に冒険できたら\Nどれほど楽しいだろうと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:23.57,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,I'm sure it would be lots \Nof fun adventuring with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だったら…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.11,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:32.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで旅ができて\Nやっぱり仲間って いいと思えた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:32.25,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,Traveling together has shown me \Nhow nice it is to be part of a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:36.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の旅が あなたたちとで\N本当によかったと思っている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:36.88,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,I'm truly grateful my last journey \Nwas made with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズさん 最後って…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.63,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Shizu, what do you mean by "last"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:45.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう うん十年も生きててね\N見た目ほど若くないから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.56,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,I've been around for decades, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.51,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,I'm not as young as I look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:49.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は？　あっ な… なんだ 冗談か
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:50.26,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Huh? O-Oh, you were just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,驚かさないでよ もう〜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.89,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Gosh, don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.35,Main,Rigur,0,0,0,,Ah, here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リグル）おっ 来た来た
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.41,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:59.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレン）お待たせ〜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:01.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ギド）待ちくたびれたでやんすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.00,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,Oh, we waited, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:05.28,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,Jeez, why do women take so long to get ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:05.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カバル）\Nったく… 女は支度が遅(おせ)えよな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズさん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.20,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Shizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）ん？\N（リグルド）どうかしましたかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.37,Main,Rigurd,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シズ）うっ！　そんな… もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:24.72,Main,Shizu,0,0,0,,Not... again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:25.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズさん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.09,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,Shizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.22,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:29.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.51,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Shizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.41,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Shizu! Shizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.98,0:09:41.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズさん！　シズさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:10.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）おっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:13.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… おい 大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.33,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Hey! Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだよ これ！\N危険手当 上乗せしてもらうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.12,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:17.31,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,We charge extra for hazard pay, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:20.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ギド）\Nだから！　それは\Nフューズの旦那に言うでやんすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:20.19,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,You should be telling Fuze that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.44,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Shizu! Shizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズさん！　シズさ〜ん！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.59,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,Shizu... Shizue Izawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:28.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズ… シズエ･イザワ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:29.15,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:31.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレン）え？\N（ギド）シズエ･イザワって…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.20,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,Isn't Shizue Izawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.42,0:10:33.50,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,...the Conqueror of Flames?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カバル）爆炎の支配者か？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:40.46,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Y-You mean the hero of the \Nguild from about 50 years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレン）\Nそ… それって\N50年くらい前 活躍したっていう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:40.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギルドの英雄よね？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズさんが？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.42,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Shizu is her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:43.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,爆炎の…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:43.65,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,The Conqueror of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:47.59,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,Wasn't she retired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 引退してんじゃ\Nなかったのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:52.76,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Rigurd, Rigur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）リグルド！　リグル！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.31,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Evacuate the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:55.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）みんなを避難させろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リグルド）しかし…\N（リグル）リムル様！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:56.64,Main,Rigurd,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:57.91,Main,Rigur,0,0,0,,Great Rimuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:10:59.07,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,That's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:10:58.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）命令だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:01.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リグルド）ははっ！　承りました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.19,Main,Rigurd,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! As you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.15,0:11:06.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）いるな？　ランガ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.30,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Are you there, Ranga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.01,Main,Ranga,0,0,0,,Right here, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ランガ）我が主(あるじ)よ ここに
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:10.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）始まったら頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.68,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Once it starts, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:11.57,Main,Ranga,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:38.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,炎の精霊… イフリート！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:38.48,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,The fire spirit, Ifrit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:41.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いないでやす\Nシズさんは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:41.60,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,There's no mistake, then. Shizu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:45.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伝説の英雄 爆炎の支配者…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:45.23,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,...the legendary hero, \Nthe Conqueror of Flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あんなの どうやっても\N勝てないんですけど？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.64,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Th-There's no way we can win \Nif we have to fight that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:52.99,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,Not a chance. We're going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:52.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理でやす…\Nあっしらは ここで死ぬんでやす
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:56.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,短い人生だったでやんすねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.78,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,My life was so short...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレン）きゃあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:23.35,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Damn it! We just built all that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:23.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nちくしょう！　せっかく\N作ったばかりだっていうのに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カバル）うう…\N（エレン）いった〜い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:25.39,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.36,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,You guys need to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nお前たちも さっさと逃げろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.68,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カバル）\Nそんなわけにはいかねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人が なんで殺意を\Nむき出しにしてんのか知らねえが…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:39.03,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,I don't know why she's \Nsuddenly out for blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:41.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちの仲間でやすよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:41.33,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,But she's one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.12,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,We can't just leave her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほっとけないわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.60,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,All right. Just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nそうか… 気をつけろよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.17,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,They're really nice guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nいいヤツらじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:53.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カバル）\Nハハ… まさか過去の英雄と\N戦う日が来ようとはね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:53.67,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,Never thought I'd see the day \Nwhen I'd fight a legendary hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ギド）\N人生 何が起こるか分かりやせんね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:56.93,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,You never know what's \Ngoing to happen in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.43,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:59.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）いくぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:07.69,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Hey! What is it you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nおい！　お前の目的は何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:14.69,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Water Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.90,0:13:14.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水刃(すいじん)！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.74,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Yeah, I should've expected that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:22.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ そりゃそうだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.14,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Icicle Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.50,0:13:29.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレン）アイシクルランス！\N（リムル）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（サラマンダー）グアア！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）おい 大丈夫なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:40.43,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Hey, you doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.06,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Just leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:41.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレン）任せてくださいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:45.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちだってね\N命張って 冒険者やってるんです！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.89,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,We've put our lives on the line \Nto be adventurers, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:50.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい 勘弁してくれよ\Nリーダーは俺だっての
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:48.67,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,Hey, gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.57,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,I'm the leader, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:51.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ しょうがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.30,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:53.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１匹は\N俺たちが受け持った！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.03,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,We've got the first one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:56.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一蓮托生(いちれんたくしょう)ってやつでさあ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:56.82,Main,Gido,0,0,0,,We're all in the same boat, as they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:14:00.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nじゃあ 任せる\Nだが 無理はするなよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.41,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,I'll leave you to it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.87,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,But don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:01.49,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:01.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.61,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Ranga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:06.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ランガ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:07.86,Main,Ranga,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:17.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）ランガ 来るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:17.84,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Ranga, here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:26.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は回避に専念しろ\N攻撃は俺がする
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:26.14,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Just concentrate on evading \Nthem! I'll do the attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ランガ）心得ました！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:27.85,Main,Ranga,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのイフリートの前に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:49.05,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,We need to take care of those \Nguys before we can face Ifrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつらだな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:52.38,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,What to do? My Water Blade \Nwill just evaporate...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？\N水刃は蒸発してしまうが…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:55.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\N俺の胃袋に入っている大量の水を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:57.80,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,But what if I shoot all the water \Nin my belly toward them at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:57.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一気にぶっかけるのは\Nどうだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.13,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者(だいけんじゃ)）\N解(かい)…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.30,Main,Text,0,0,0,,Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.45,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,Expulsion of great amounts \Nof water is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.68,sign_21564_164_Expulsion_of_gre,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(1071,1)}Expulsion of\Ngreat amounts of water\Nis possible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:03.35,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,When it makes contact with a Salamander,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:05.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者）\Nサラマンダーとの接触により\N水蒸気爆発が生じます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:05.35,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,it will cause an explosion of steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.81,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,Take this action?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:06.81,sign_21718_168_Take_this_action,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(605,1)}Take this action?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:11.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\N水蒸気爆発！\Nそれでサラマンダーは消滅するか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.87,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,An explosion of steam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:11.21,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Will that destroy the Salamanders?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.38,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,It is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者）可能です\N（リムル）おお！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:18.07,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,However, the force of the blast may \Ndestroy the surrounding area, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者）\Nただし 爆発の威力で\Nこの辺り一帯も吹き飛ぶでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:20.69,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Well, what's the point in that, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）アホか！　意味ねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（サラマンダー）グガア！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.35,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Icicle Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アイシクルランス！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:29.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グガアアア！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.75,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Her attack is working, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:32.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nあの攻撃 効いてるんじゃね？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.08,0:15:36.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者）\N魔法攻撃は精霊に対して有効です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:36.20,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,Magic attacks are effective against spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:37.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）てことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:37.97,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:39.40,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Ranga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:40.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）ランガ！\N（ランガ）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.21,Main,Ranga,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:46.01,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Eren! Fire that attack at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nエレン！\Nそれ 俺に向けて撃ってくれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:49.89,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,What?! Um, I don't know if I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:49.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はえっ？\Nえっと そんなこと言われても…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.77,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Just do it! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）頼む！　早く！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:54.27,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Don't complain to me later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（エレン）\Nあとで\N文句 言わないでくださいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:58.27,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,Icicle Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.69,0:15:58.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アイシクルラ〜ンス！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:08.66,Main,Eren,0,0,0,,What?! My magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:08.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うえ〜！　私の魔法が…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.21,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,Notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:10.33,sign_21718_168_Take_this_action,Text,0,0,0,,Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:13.16,Main,Great,0,0,0,,Analysis of Icicle Lance successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:13.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者）\Nアイシクルランスの解析に\N成功しました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:13.16,sign_23290_189_Analysis,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(193,1)}Analysis
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.16,sign_23290_189_Analysis,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,180)\fad(151,1)}Successful
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:13.96,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.52,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Icicle Shotgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）アイシクルショット！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:35.66,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:35.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:43.99,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,I'll get that one, too—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:43.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）そいつも 俺が…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.58,Main,Kaval,0,0,0,,It's gonna blow itself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カバル）こいつ 自爆を…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カバル･ギド）ぐわあああ！\N（エレン）きゃあああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.59,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you o—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）おい！　大丈夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.63,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Nope, they're not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃないな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:05.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カバル）うっ うぐ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:10.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nランガ この３人を安全な場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:10.51,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Ranga, get these three someplace safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ランガ）しかし…\N（リムル）行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:11.74,Main,Ranga,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:12.69,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:16.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ランガ）\Nはっ！　仰せのままに…\Nご武運を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:15.18,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,As you command, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.27,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Please be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.89,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:17.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）安心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.79,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,I'll take down Ifrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イフリートは俺が倒す
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:37.54,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Okay, now we can fight without holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:37.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nさてと…\Nこれで 心おきなく戦えるな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:07.65,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Take this! Icicle Shotgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くらえ！　アイシクルショット！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:16.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nいける！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:16.66,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,It's gonna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.28,Main,Ranga,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ランガ）我が主…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:46.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）ぐわあああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:51.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\Nああ…\Nもっと やりようがあった気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:51.20,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,There should've been \Nsomething else I could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:55.20,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,I can't believe I fell into the enemy's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:55.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の思惑どおり\N罠(わな)にはまったなんて最悪だ〜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:19:00.46,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Instead of talking about seals, \NI should've hit them with Black Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:19:00.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,封印とか言わないで\N黒稲妻(くろいなずま)をぶち込んでおけば…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:03.73,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,And after I was just reincarnated \Nhere as a slime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかくスライムに転生したのに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:06.70,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Is this really the end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでか〜！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:08.93,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,It was a short life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:11.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,短い人生… いや スライム生だった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:11.82,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,rather, a short slife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:17.06,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't seem \Nto be taking much damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ていうか\Nダメージが なかなか来ないな？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:19.73,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,How long is it gonna take?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:21.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てか 遅すぎない？\Nじらしプレイ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:21.15,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Is this some kind of tease?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:22.88,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:22.73,sign_27864_219_Answer,Text,0,0,0,,Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.44,sign_27896_221_As_Previously_St,Text,0,0,0,,As Previously Stated
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.44,sign_27896_222_Thermal_Fluctuat,Text,0,0,0,,Thermal Fluctuation Resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.51,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,Due to "Thermal Fluctuation Resistance,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者）\N“熱変動耐性”の効果により…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:28.90,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,fire attacks are being \Nautomatically nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:28.90,sign_27896_222_Thermal_Fluctuat,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs30}Fire attacks are being\N\Nautomatically nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:29.98,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者）\Nハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:31.20,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.61,0:19:33.75,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Hey, why do you sound exasperated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.86,0:19:33.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）なんか あきれてない？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:38.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあいい\N炎が無効化できるのであれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:38.08,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Oh, well. If I can nullify fire attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.22,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,this'll be easy mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽勝モードだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.15,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,It's all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:44.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果オーライ！　いや 全て…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.46,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,In fact, everything is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:46.42,Italics,Rimuru,0,0,0,,according to plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.67,0:19:46.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,計画どおり
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:12.27,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Did you just do something to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）今 何かしたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:23.09,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,I underestimated you, but not as \Nmuch as you underestimated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）\N俺も お前のことをナメていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:23.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も 俺をナメ過ぎだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.20,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のターンだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:36.35,Italics_Top,Great,0,0,0,,Use unique skill "Predator"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:36.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者）\Nユニークスキル“捕食者”を\N使用しますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:38.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（リムル）イエス！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.32,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:56.55,Main,Rimuru,0,0,0,,Shizu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:56.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,シズさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:21.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ヴェルドラ）\N観念せよ イフリート
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:21.18,Main,Veldora,0,0,0,,Give up, Ifrit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ヴェルドラ）\N貴様に この空間は破れん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.34,0:21:32.11,Main,Veldora,0,0,0,,You cannot break out of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:39.06,Main,Veldora,0,0,0,,You are no match for Rimuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:39.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ヴェルドラ）\N貴様のかなう相手ではないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.95,Main,Veldora,0,0,0,,He is my sworn friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:41.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,リムルは我の盟友ぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:48.05,Main,Veldora,0,0,0,,I am the Storm Dragon, Veldora Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.45,0:21:48.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我は\N暴風竜ヴェルドラ･テンペスト
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.33,Main,Veldora,0,0,0,,It would be my pleasure to face you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:51.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心ゆくまで相手をしてやろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.80,0:22:02.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハッハッハッハ！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.82,0:23:38.48,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0,0,0,,Next time, "Inherited Will."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:38.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（大賢者）\N次回「受け継がれる想(おも)い」
